quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  13,6,Futhi bakujahela ebubini ngaphambi kobuhle futhi sezadlula ngaphambilini kwabo izijeziso ezifana (nalokho abakujahayo) futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho ingumnikazi wentethelelo kubantu ekungalungini kwabo futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho inzima ekujeziseni
  13,7,"Futhilaboabangakholwangabathi,“kunganikungehliselwanga phansi kuyena uphawu oluvela eNkosini yakhe na?” Kuphela wena ungumxwayisi futhi kulabo nalabo bantu kunomholi"
  13,8,UMvelinqangi uyakwazi lokho okukhulelwe ibona bonke abesifazane kanye nalokho izizalo ezilahlekelwa yikona (okusuke kungakalungeli ukuthi kungazalwa) kanye nalokho ezikwandisayo (izizalo) futhi zonke izinto kuyena zilinganisiwe
  13,9,"Uyisazi sokungabonwayo nokubonwayo, mkhulu uphakeme"
  13,10,Kuyefana (kuyena) noma ngabe omunye wenu ufihla inkulumo noma nalowo oyivezayo kanye nalowo ozifihlayo ebusuku bese ehamba emini
  13,11,Ezakhe izingelosi eziqaphelayo ngaphambili (komuntu ngamunye) nangemva kwakhe ziyamlondoloza ngempoqo kaMvelinqangi akasiguquli isimo sabantu kuze kube ilapho beguqula lokho okusemiphefumulweni yabo futhi uma uMvelinqangi eqonde okubi ebantwini akekho ongakuphindisela emumva futhi abanaye umvikeli ngaphandle kwakhe
  13,12,Nguyena onikhombisa umbani odala ukwesaba nethemba futhi (nguyena) oletha amafu asindayo
  13,13,Nokuduma kuyamphakamisa ngodumo lwakhe kanye nezingelosi (ziyamdumisa) ngenxa yokumesaba futhi athumele ukushaya konyazi ashaye ngawo lowo amthandayo ngenkathi bona bephikisana ngoMvelinqangi kanti yena uphakeme ngamandla futhi unzima ekujeziseni